Package jde.juci.test

Interface Summary
Callback Declare/expose a getMessage method for calling by elisp through JUCI.
Echo Declare/expose a couple of simple methods for calling from elisp through JUCI.
Prompt A test JUCI interface to prompt back to Emacs for user input.
 

Class Summary
CallbackImpl Testing/example class for calling back to elisp through JUCI.
EchoImpl Simple implementation of the Echo interface.
